== TO SUBSCRIBE/UNSUBSCRIBE ==

So then there was that thing about a year ago you told yourself you'd
probably never ever do at least not for a long long time and maybe never
at least not in this lifetime because no way is that really your style
or your soul's modus operandi or your ego's manner of marauding but
which now you look at one year later and sort of go wow well why the
hell not maybe I should just do it I mean life really is too damn short
not to peel back the layers of your own personal accumulated
self-delusional bullshit and question just why it is you believe what
you believe or inhibit what you inhibit because otherwise the
alternative is of course karmic stagnation and self-indulgent
masturbatory solipsistic whining about why nothing ever changes when all
you've really got to do is tune in and turn on and
http://sfgate.com/newsletters/.

