== DISCLAIMER ==

Sometimes it is helpful to imagine yourself to be some sort of
delectable juice supped by gods. Stop it already with the sneering and
the popping of the gum and the too much makeup and the spitting.
Sometimes all you really do need is a really nice pair of shoes and some
quality sunglasses and a nice glass of wine and the world feels all
delicious and right. If this is not what you expected, please alter your
expectations. No such thing as random coincidence. No such thing as too
much lubricant.


